snippet.title: Emergency Call 112 - The Fire Fighting Simulation 2 | Official Trailer | Aerosoft
snippet.description:
Out now for PC | https://store.steampowered.com/app/785770/Notruf_112__Die_Feuerwehr_Simulation_2/

Emergency Call 112 - The Fire Fighting Simulation 2 is the consequent further development of the successful first part, which lets every Firefighter Fan experience the way a professional fire brigade works. The second part was also developed in cooperation with the Mülheim fire department and the support of our active Community. 

For more news and informations follow us:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Aerosoft​
Twitter: https://twitter.com/aerosoftgmbh​
